<h1>Payment pending verification</h1>

<p><%= @payment.user.display_name %> submitted a bank transfer for <%= @payment.membership_plan.name %> (<%= @payment.beneficiary_label %>).</p>

<p>
  Amount: <%= number_to_currency(@payment.transfer_amount || @payment.amount, unit: "¥", precision: 0) %><br>
  Transfer date: <%= @payment.transferred_on&.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %><br>
  Reference name: <%= @payment.transfer_reference_name %>
</p>

<p>Please verify the transfer in the MSJ Portal and approve the payment after confirming the bank account.</p>
